findings.title: Rounding error
findings.description: Take fee calculations uses division first which can cause rounding errors due to Solidity's lack of floating points.

findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function manualSync() and setAutomatedMarketMakerPair() uses the loop to iterate through _makerPairs list. Function will be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there will be a long list.

findings.title: Arithmetic accuracy
findings.description: Rounding error due to division before multiplication.
